The skyline of NYC from my new apartment window is surreal. Japan feels like a dream now. Time to dive into this new chapter with all I've learned.

Turning 22 in NYC, surrounded by skyscrapers instead of temples. Reflecting on my journey, grateful for every experience. Here's to coding breakthroughs, new connections, and figuring out my next move.
